In medium saucepan, combine water, rice, cinnamon stick, orange rind and salt. Bring to a boil, reduce heat; cover and simmer 15 minutes. Stir in EAGLE BRAND(R). Cook uncovered over low heat, stirring frequently 25 minutes or until rice is tender. Remove cinnamon stick and orange rind. Cool. (Pudding will thicken as it cools). Stir in raisins or nuts (optional). Garnish with cinnamon. Serve warm or chilled. Store leftovers covered in refrigerator.